        <content><![CDATA[ <h1 class="title topictitle1">Indicator sources</h1>  <div class="body conbody">  <p class="p"><span class="ph">Indicator sources define the set of records to evaluate when   collecting indicator scores.</span></p>  <p class="p">Indicator sources are based on a facts table, such as Incident, and may   specify filter conditions to limit the included records. One indicator source can be used by   multiple indicators.</p>  <p class="p">Typically, the indicator tracks the situation on a certain date. The   conditions should include a date-related filter, such as    <span class="ph uicontrol">[Opened][on][Today]</span>. Indicators collected less frequently might specify a   larger date range, such as <span class="ph uicontrol">[Closed][on][This month]</span>.</p> </div>]]></content>
